SELECT [o3].[Id], [o3].[BranchId], [o3].[CashbackPercent], [o3].[CashbackUsedAmount], [o3].[CreatedById], [o3].[CreatedOn], [o3].[CustomerAddressId], [o3].[CustomerId], [o3].[CustomerIdentifier], [o3].[DeliveryFees], [o3].[DiscountAmount], [o3].[GrandTotal], [o3].[IsDeleted], [o3].[LastUpdatedById], [o3].[LastUpdatedOn], [o3].[OrderDate], [o3].[OrderNumber], [o3].[SubTotal], [o2].[Id], [o2].[OrderId], [o2].[Status], [o2].[TimeToCompleteStatus], [o2].[Timestamp]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [o].[Id], [o].[BranchId], [o].[CashbackPercent], [o].[CashbackUsedAmount], [o].[CreatedById], [o].[CreatedOn], [o].[CustomerAddressId], [o].[CustomerId], [o].[CustomerIdentifier], [o].[DeliveryFees], [o].[DiscountAmount], [o].[GrandTotal], [o].[IsDeleted], [o].[LastUpdatedById], [o].[LastUpdatedOn], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[OrderNumber], [o].[SubTotal]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[CustomerIdentifier] = @__customerIdentifier_0 AND COALESCE((
        SELECT TOP(1) [o0].[Status]
        FROM [OrderStatuses] AS [o0]
        WHERE [o].[Id] = [o0].[OrderId]
        ORDER BY [o0].[Timestamp] DESC), 0) <> 3 AND COALESCE((
        SELECT TOP(1) [o1].[Status]
        FROM [OrderStatuses] AS [o1]
        WHERE [o].[Id] = [o1].[OrderId]
        ORDER BY [o1].[Timestamp] DESC), 0) <> 4
    ORDER BY [o].[CreatedOn] DESC
) AS [o3]
LEFT JOIN [OrderStatuses] AS [o2] ON [o3].[Id] = [o2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o3].[CreatedOn] DESC, [o3].[Id]
